quran[63]{c,v,t}:
  76,19,"Bazo kikuzwa n’imisore isharije, ubabonye womengo n’ubutare bwitiriwe Ilulu za sanzajwe"
  76,20,"Ubonye ibirimwo, uzoca ubona imigisha hamwe n’ubwami bw’Imana bunini cane"
  76,21,"Hejuru yabo barafise impuzu zihwahutse z’ibara ry’urwatsi rubisi, hamwe n’izindi zihwahutse ziremereye gatoyi, kandi bazokwambikwa ingori z’umwakaka, n’Umuremyi wabo azoba nywesha ibinyobwa vyiza cane"
  76,22,Mu vy’ukuri iyi niyo mpembo yanyu yibijanye n’ibikorwa vyanyu vyemewe
  76,23,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twakumanuriye iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu ibice bice
  76,24,"Rero n’urindire intahe y’Umuremyi wawe, kandi ntugamburukire umwe muribo mubagira ibicumuro canke uwuhakana Imana yiwe y’ukuri"
  76,25,Ni wibuke izina ry’Umuremyi wawe mu gitondo no ku mugoroba
  76,26,"Mw’ijoro naho uyunamire ushize umutwe wawe hasi, kandi uyi ninahaze mw’ijoro mumwanya muremure"
  76,27,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\taba\tbantu\tbikundira\tubuzima\tbwo\tngaha\tkw’Isi\tgusa, n’ugusiga inyuma yabo umusi ugoye cane kuribo"
  76,28,"Twebwe twabaremye n’ugushira mwo ubushobozi mubihimba vy’imibiri yabo, dushatse twoshobora kuzana abandi bantu atari bo bameze nkabo"
  76,29,"Mu vy’ukuri iki n’icibutso, rero kuwushaka azofata inzira imushikana ku Muremyi wiwe"
  76,30,"Kandi ntimushobora gushaka icarico cose Imana itabishatse, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  76,31,"Yinjiza uwo yishakiye mu migisha yayo, naba hemukiye imitima yabo yarabateguriye ibihano bibabaza cane"
  77,1,Ndarahiye kumiyaga izanwa buhoro buhoro
  77,2,No kumiyaga ihinda kunguvu nyinshi cane
  77,3,"No kumiyaga igurura ibicu, ikabigurura nkuko Imana ibishaka"
  77,4,Iga tandukanisha kure na kure ivyo bicu
  77,5,Ndarahiye kuba Marayika bashikiriza ubutumwa bw’Imana ku ntumwa z’Imana
  77,6,Mugukura impamvu kanaka canke gutuza
  77,7,Mu vy’ukuri ibi mwemerewe ntankeka bizoshika
  77,8,Mugihe inyenyeri zizo hanagurwa imico yazo
  77,9,N’amajuru igihe azo manyagurika
  77,10,N’imisozi igihe izo vungagurika
  77,11,N’intumwa z’Imana igihe zizo kwegeranywa
  77,12,Ni k’umusi uwuhe bagenewe ico gihe
  77,13,N’umusi w’intahe y’ukuri
  77,14,None n’igiki kizo kumenyesha uwo musi w’intahe y’ukuri
  77,15,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,16,Mbega ntitwahoneje abantu ba kera burundu
  77,17,Hanyuma dukurikiza ko abandi bantu
  77,18,Uko niko tuzobagira abandi bazoba bari mumakosa
  77,19,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,20,Mbega ntitwabaremye mumazi ahoya hoya
  77,21,Hanyuma tuyashira ahantu haturuye
  77,22,Kugeza kukiringo kizwi
  77,23,"Natwe tugereranya umwanya w’ukuboneka kw’ikibondo, natwe ni beza mukugereranya"
  77,24,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,25,Mbega twebwe ntitwagize iy’Isi kugira ngo twegeranye abantu bose
  77,26,Mubiri bizima hamwe n’ivyapfuye
  77,27,"No\tmuriyo\tduhashira\tmwo\timisozi\tmire\tmire\titsimbataye\tneza\thasi n’ukubanywesha amazi meza y’umusarara"
  77,28,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,29,Ni mugende kuri vya bihano mwahora muhakana
  77,30,Ni mugende muri ca gitutu c’umuriro gifise impande zitatu
  77,31,"Ntikibapfuka\tico\tgitutu\tcanke\tntikibahengeshanya\tn’ukwaka\tkuwo muriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu"
  77,32,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tuwo\tmuriro\tudahera\tutanga\timishwarara\tyawo\tingana nk’amazu"
  77,33,Nkuko womengo n’ingamiya ifise ibara ry’umuhondo
  77,34,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,35,Uno musi n’umusi waho ata nakimwe bavuga
  77,36,Kandi ntibazo habwa uruhusha kugira ngo bisigure
  77,37,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,38,"Uwu\tn’umusi\tw’intahe\ty’ukuri,\ttwabegeranije\tmwese\thamwe n’ababayeho imbere yanyu"
  77,39,Ni mwaba mufise izindi ngeso ni muzigire hejuru yanje
  77,40,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,41,"Ntankeka\taba\tninahaza\tImana\tyabo\ty’ukuri\tbazoba\tbari\tmu\tbitutu n’imyonga"
  77,42,N’ivyamwa bakunda
  77,43,"Ni mufungure kandi munywe n’akanya muneza ntangere, kubera ivyo mwahora mugira"
  77,44,Uku rero niko duhemba abagira ineza
  77,45,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,46,"Ni mufungure kandi mwinezereze gatoyi gusa, mu vy’ukuri mwebwe muri abononyi"
  77,47,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,48,"Babwiwe bati :- ni mupfukame, ntibigera bapfukama namba"
  77,49,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,50,Mbega n’ibiganiro nyabaki inyuma yibi biganiro vy’amajambo y’Imana matagatifu ya Qur’ani bazo kwemera